    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "An ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.scenekit/documentation/SceneKit/SCNAudioSource",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " object represents a distinct source of audio (for example, a sound file) that can be reused and shared by many player objects. Use this method to create an audio player from such a source. When you use this method, SceneKit creates an audio player for the specified ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.scenekit/documentation/SceneKit/SCNAudioSource",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " object or, if an audio player for that source already exists and is not in use, SceneKit reuses the existing player object.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If instead you want to attach a more complex audio setup to a position in your scene—such as a mixer that varies several audio inputs in response to user input—build that setup using ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/AVFAudio/AVAudioNode",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " objects and create a player for it with the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.scenekit/documentation/SceneKit/SCNAudioPlayer/audioPlayerWithAVAudioNode:",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
